    {
      "description": "<p>You create a healing elixir in a simple vial that appears in your hand. The elixir retains its potency for the duration or until it's consumed, at which point the vial vanishes.</p> <p class=\"indent\">As an action, a creature can drink the elixir or administer it to another creature. The drinker regains 2d4 + 2 hit points.</p>",
